    rating: "Good"
    comments: "Visual Effects"
  }
  pacing: "Pacing is pretty fast as it goes through 3 different scenarios (but this was intentional as the editing style helped make it more of a thriller)"
  climax: "Climax in each of the three scenarios is carried out well and shows what would happen if the story played out that way"
  tone: "Tone is very similar to other action-thrillers (sometimes even feeling like a shootout movie like John Wick)"
  final_notes: "Saw the world premiere at SXSW"
  overall: "Overall, a very unique movie that uses sharp technicals, especially editing and cinematography, and fast-paced direction to create an engaging thriller as we see the same story told in three different perspectives"
